{"tid":648363,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[月經]一人一件好鐘意食嘅野","createTime":"2018-04-30T15:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T07:15:32.000Z","uid":84177,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"954d4ac06f7b050f2267b7dbe738919500cb047c","tid":648363,"uid":84177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:26:45.000Z","msg":"有次同個fd去灣仔食泰國野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,食飽就思甜慾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以就去左711 見到香芋糯米糍,我地覺得好味就買左一盒兩粒<br />\n<br />\n我同個朋友都好餓,初頭係佢食先 點知我又好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  跟住我地不知不覺咁一齊食一粒 一齊lam同一粒 之後開始黎料,粒野越黎越濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  開始時大家都只係想食糯米糍 點知越黎越濕 越濕越想要多粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係我嘗試咬開同一粒糯米糍<br />\n<br />\n於是我fd忍唔住想屌我話無儀態 點知試左好耐都分開唔到 之後轉佢咬都咬唔開 越咬越濕<br />\n<br />\n最後我地無幫大家 自己搞掂自己果粒野 完事之後仲自己訓 到第二日大家就當無事發生過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:好鍾意食糯米糍"},{"pid":"2be1525c4af7848d0a3d6f5fe86ff68a52c7313e","tid":648363,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:27:49.000Z","msg":"新地筒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e06e661629ee5071a2634c667693615ec481d86","tid":648363,"uid":6783,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:28:04.000Z","msg":"GAY撚到 大家唔好回"},{"pid":"5670f6083e266d94b035a0460b58c9002d71b19b","tid":648363,"uid":84177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bff3b8f2769fca348e2b30a2794f8a9ed96eff6","tid":648363,"uid":166301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"954d4ac06f7b050f2267b7dbe738919500cb047c","tid":648363,"uid":84177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:26:45.000Z","msg